==English==
===Noun===
'''[[Jewish]] [[lightning]]'''
# Supposed cause of a [[fire]] which is in fact deliberately lit by the property owner in order to benefit from [[insurance]] or similar such as destruction of documents.
#: 1996: ''The insurance companies, many of which were Jewish, referred to "Jewish lightning" when unfortunate fires burned down warehouses in the East End.'' &mdash; [[w:John le Carré|John le Carré]], interviewed at salon.com [http://www.salon.com/weekly/lecarre961021.html]